    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >感谢的所有&quot;氪佬&quot;对《中国式网游》的支持和期待，全新DLC&quot;彩票模式&quot;已正式推出</h2><br>应社群内&quot;氪佬&quot;们的声音，说喜欢刮刮乐，想玩刮彩票，现在它来了！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >我们把&quot;刮刮乐彩票&quot;做成了一个全新独立的模式，新增10余张全新不同面值不同玩法的刮刮乐供大家游玩，且融入了与老板&quot;合作方案&quot;的轻度玩法。下一个&quot;百万大奖&quot;会不会是你呢？</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334700/extras/c5cdf4150eeefa238115e266b8a11820.avif?t=1734663026\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334700/extras_big/c5cdf4150eeefa238115e266b8a11820.avif?t=1734663026 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><br>“彩票模式“DLC新内容汇总如下：<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一、一个全新的独立新模式</h2>大家可以在游戏主页面右边处，选择&quot;彩票模式&quot;进入新模式<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334700/extras/8799e3f3c3899fab40dada3422cdc26a.avif?t=1734663026\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334700/extras_big/8799e3f3c3899fab40dada3422cdc26a.avif?t=1734663026 width=800 height=450 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >二、全新独立的排行榜系统</h2>我们为新的彩票模式增加了一个全新的排行榜系统，祝大家&quot;欧气满满&quot;！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334700/extras/51052136cd83fd130923952fd7032b30.avif?t=1734663026\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334700/extras_big/51052136cd83fd130923952fd7032b30.avif?t=1734663026 width=800 height=450 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >三、新增总计10种 彩票种类</h2>共计新增全新的彩票新玩法：<br>1、5元——大灌篮刮刮乐<br>2、5元——欢乐3个8<br>3、10元——蓝宝石<br>4、10元——超级好运<br>5、20元——发大财<br>6、20元——秘境寻宝<br>7、30元——财源滚滚<br>8、300——金鸡报喜<br>9、50元——大金龙<br>10、50元——超级6<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334700/extras/7c180434281956c52acc919bb35b5495.avif?t=1734663026\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334700/extras_big/7c180434281956c52acc919bb35b5495.avif?t=1734663026 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334700/extras/7037e6cc1a78f4db770f60ac81c02fdf.avif?t=1734663026\" width=500 height=992 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >四、新增彩票模式新动画</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334700/extras/6deec1a547d3d4fdfa5048a2e2de9327.avif?t=1734663026\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334700/extras_big/6deec1a547d3d4fdfa5048a2e2de9327.avif?t=1734663026 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><br>最后非常感谢大家的等待，DLC推出不代表游戏停止更新，我们还会持续优化问题，认真听取玩家的反馈更新新内容。",
